<h2 id="foreword">Foreword</h2>

<ul>
  <li><em>“Where there is no hope, it is incumbent on us to invent it.”</em> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Camus" class="note-highlight">learn more</a>.</li>
