<h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><em>“…as Michelangelo put it, what’s already living within the marble.”</em> is based on 2 quotes from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelangelo" class="note-highlight">Michelangelo Buonarroti</a>:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <p><em>“The sculpture is already complete within the marble block, before I start my work. It is already there, I just have to chisel away the superfluous material.”</em></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><em>“I saw the angel in the marble and carved until I set him free.”</em></p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

